<u>Amateka</u> 

Evelyne Umurerwa n'Umunyarwandakazi wavutse mu mwaka (1977) aho  yavukiye mukarere ka Nyarugenge<ref>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/section/read/64059</ref> umugi wa kigali ni mwene  Eduard Nsababera na Blandine Mukasekuru,yashakanye nuwitwa Jean-Marie Uwizeye kutari (8/1/200) uy mugabo babyaranye abana 2 b'abakobwa.

<u>Amashuri yize</u>

Evelyne Umurerwa  yize amashuri yisumbuye kukigo cya Centre Islamiques de l'Enseignments  Secondaires de Kigali (CIESK) Akomereza amashuri ya kaminuza  kukigo  cya Kigali independent yiga ishami ryimimibanire.

<u>Akazi yakoze</u>

Umurerwa n'umunyarwandakazi w'umunyamakuru ukorera Radio na television by'Urwanda<ref>https://igihe.com/serivisi/special-pages/womens-month/inkuru/article/urugendo-rwa-umurerwa-evelyne-umaze-imyaka-isaga-17-asoma-amakuru-kuri</ref>  kuva mu mwaka (1998) aho abimazemo imyaka irenga 20,yakoze kuri radio na television by'igihugu agisoza kwiga amashuri yisumbuye nyuma anaminuza akora ako kazi kubunyamakuru ,mu kazi akora kuri television 'Urwanda yibanda kubiganiro bijyanye niterambere cyane cyane  ryigitsina gore aho yakoze ikiganiro cyitwa Iterambere ry'Abagore muri ikigihe arimo gukora ikiganiro cya Tinyuka urashoboye kuri television y'Urwanda aho iki kiganiro gishishikariza  abakore kwitinyuka bagakora imishinga mitoya bahereye kugishoro gitonya ibi bizabarinda guhora batergereje ibivuye kubagabo babo bakigira ubwabo.

i<u>byo akunda gukora  mugihe cyokuruhuka</u>

Mugihe cyo kuruhuka igihe Evelyne atari mukazi akunda kuba arikumwe n'umuryango we ndetse ninshuti ze,akunda kandi kujya koga,gym na sauna aho abikorera ku Umubano Hotel.
